	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not "an actual NES" but "an actual Nintendo MMC3 chip". An actual NES connected to a Game Pak containing an MMC3-clone CPLD that uses a different algorithm for the scanline counter (perhaps based on PPU A13 not A12) should run the game as intended. But then we first have to figure out how to make an MMC3-clone CPLD in the first place.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


